This directory contains TSPLIB, a library of traveling salesman and
related problem instances.

TSPLIB95 can be freely distributed for research purposes.

A full documentation about the library is given in the PostScript
file DOC.ps.

Contributions to this library are strongly encouraged. Potential 
contributors should provide their data files in the appropriate format and 
contact

     Gerhard Reinelt
     Institut fuer Angewandte Mathematik
     Universitaet Heidelberg
     Im Neuenheimer Feld 294
     D-69120 Heidelberg
     Germany

     Tel.   (6221) 56 3171
     Fax    (6221) 56 5634
     E-Mail  Gerhard.Reinelt@iwr.Uni-Heidelberg.DE

Comments or error messages as well as new bounds or optimal solutions
should also be reported to this address.
    
